init_text: Humans once wielded formidable magical power. But with over 7 billion of us on the planet now, Mana has spread far too thinly to have any effect. When hostile aliens reduce humanity to a mere fraction, the survivors discover an old power has begun to reawaken once again.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The magic of the old gods is returning.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They are surprised when the Gods do appear.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They are even more surprised when the Gods tell them that they have no intention of teaching them how to use Mana.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The humans have to learn how to use it on their own.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The Gods disappear, leaving the humans to their own devices.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They have to work harder to be worthy of Mana.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The humans decide that they have to learn to live in harmony with the planet.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They have to learn to live in harmony with the animals, plants, and elements.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They have to learn to live in harmony with each other.
